# Bodyly | Gentle BMI Calculator

A soft and friendly BMI calculator built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.  
Designed to help users understand their BMI with gentle guidance and educational context.

## Features
- Calculate BMI using weight (kg) and height (cm)
- Friendly color-coded BMI results
- Reset option to start fresh
- Educational page explaining BMI and ranges
- Soft, accessible UI design

## Tech Stack
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Google Fonts

## Project Structure
/bodyly/
  index.html
  bmi-info.html
  /css/style.css
  /js/script.js
  /assets/

